---
import Section from "../ui/Section.astro";
import Button from "../ui/Button.astro";
---

<Section id="faq" title="FAQ">
  <div class="faq">
    <details class="faq__item" open>
      <summary>When will I see results?</summary>
      <p class="muted">Consistency matters. Results vary based on habits, starting point, and frequency (placeholder).</p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq__item">
      <summary>Is it safe?</summary>
      <p class="muted">Gentle approach. Stop if you feel pain. This is not medical advice (placeholder).</p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq__item">
      <summary>Do I need equipment?</summary>
      <p class="muted">No. Just your hands and consistency.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq__item">
      <summary>How do I access the course?</summary>
      <p class="muted">You purchase on the platform; access is granted there. This site links to it.</p>
    </details>

    <div class="faq__cta">
      <Button href="#free-tips" variant="primary" data-ff-event="scroll_click" data-ff-content="faq_to_free_tips">
        Get the free mini-guide
      </Button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .faq { display: grid; gap: 12px; }

    .faq__item {
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
      padding: 14px;
    }

    summary {
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      list-style: none;
      outline: none;
    }

    summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }

    summary::after {
      content: "+";
      float: right;
      color: rgba(238, 240, 255, 0.7);
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    details[open] summary::after { content: "â€“"; }

    .faq__item p { margin: 10px 0 0; }
    .faq__cta { margin-top: 6px; }
  </style>
</Section>
